---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

export const prerender = true;
---

<Layout lang="en" title="About InfoLead | AI-Native Solutions for Canadian SMBs">
  <main>
    <div class="tag">
      <div class="dot"></div>
      OUR DNA
    </div>

    <h1 class="grad">AI-Native. Lean. Impact-Driven.</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      We are not a traditional IT agency. We are an AI-native company built to arm Canadian SMBs with unfair technological advantages.
    </p>

    <div class="content-wrapper">
      
      <div class="story-section">
        <h2>Founding Mission</h2>
        <p>
          For over a decade, traditional software development has been a luxury reserved for large enterprises. IT outsourcing agencies operate on a labor-intensive model—billing by the hour, deploying large teams, and taking months to deliver. For local Canadian businesses, the barrier to entry was simply too high.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="story-section">
        <h2>The Lean & AI-Powered Leverage</h2>
        <p>
          InfoLead was rebooted with a completely different philosophy. Operating as a lean, AI-empowered technology firm, we eliminated the bloat of traditional tech agencies. We don't just write code; we deploy "Productized AI Employees" that solve real business bottlenecks instantly.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="story-section">
        <h2>Local Expertise. Global Reach.</h2>
        <p>
          As a registered Federal Corporation based in the Greater Toronto Area, we deeply understand the operational challenges of North American businesses. We bridge the gap between cutting-edge global AI and your specific industry needs.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="cta" style="margin-top: 60px;">
      <a href="/en/contact" class="btn btn-primary">
        Build Your AI Workforce 
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 80px 32px 120px;
  }
  .content-wrapper {
    margin-top: 60px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 48px;
  }
  .story-section h2 {
    font-family: "Instrument Serif", serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    color: #F5F7FA;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    padding-bottom: 12px;
    font-weight: normal;
  }
  .story-section p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
</style>